column18: Due to COVID restrictions, visitation to any of the Canadian Arcitic glacier monitoring sites was not possible in the spring of 2020. Hence, the glaciological mass-balance had to be derived based on the spring surveys in 2019 [2019-04-08] and in 2021 [2021-04-08].
